      • setTripRecordingEnabled

        public final void setTripRecordingEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Set the persistent state of trip recording: enabled or disabled.

        Note that setting this value will only take affect upon initialization of InrixCore.

        Parameters:
        enabled - true for enabled, false for disabled.

      • isTripRecordingEnabled

        public final boolean isTripRecordingEnabled()
        Get the persistent state of trip recording or the value defined by Configuration.Builder.tripRecordingEnabledByDefault(boolean) if no value has been set via Configuration.setTripRecordingEnabled(boolean).
        Returns:
        true if enabled, false if disabled.

      • setCalendarSyncEnabled

        public final void setCalendarSyncEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Set the persistent state of calendar synchronization: enabled or disabled.
        Note that setting this value will only take affect upon initialization of InrixCore.

        Caller must hold Manifest.permission.READ_CALENDAR otherwise Calendar synchronization will be disabled.

        Parameters:
        enabled - true for enabled, false for disabled.

      • isCalendarSyncEnabled

        public final boolean isCalendarSyncEnabled()
        Get the persistent state of calendar synchronization or the value defined by Configuration.Builder.calendarSyncEnabledByDefault(boolean) if no value has been set via Configuration.setCalendarSyncEnabled(boolean).
        Returns:
        true if enabled, false if disabled.

      • isCalendarDefaultNotificationEnabled

        public boolean isCalendarDefaultNotificationEnabled()
        Get whether push notifications are enabled by default for calendar events.
        Returns:
        true if enabled, false if disabled.

      • getCalendarDefaultNotificationTimne

        public int getCalendarDefaultNotificationTimne()
        Get the default notification time (in minutes) for calendar events.

        Note that this setting is only relevant if push notifications are enabled by default for calendar events.

        Returns:
        Notification time in minutes.

      • isUserLocationMonitoringEnabled

        public boolean isUserLocationMonitoringEnabled()
        Get whether or not the user's location should be monitored.
        Returns:
        true for enabled, false for disabled.
        See Also:
